        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "アメリカンスタイルの\nバーベキュー、ですか？",
            "enText": "American-style barbeque, you say?",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": 4847710579665604722,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "イエス！　グラスもアメリカ出身！\nあの味が恋しくなりまセンカ～？",
            "enText": "Yes! You're from America too, aren'cha? \nDon'cha miss the taste of a good barbeque?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": 4851939014206091344,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "うーん、私はどちらかというと、\r\n和食の方が好きなので～……。",
            "enText": "Hm… To be honest, I personally \nprefer Japanese food.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": 4408823261257732304,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "ワオ、そうだったんデスカ！？",
            "enText": "Whoa, no kiddin'?!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": -1156241200620810301,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "はい。よく作るのも\n和食ですし……。",
            "enText": "Yes. Most of the food I prepare myself \nis also Japanese in style…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "pathId": 3090684945855035495,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "オウ……。",
            "enText": "Oh…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "pathId": 2704463519864317165,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "……でも、たまにはアメリカンな\n食事も楽しそうですね～。",
            "enText": "Although… having American \nonce in a while would be nice.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "pathId": -5446913421326710079,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "お邪魔させてください、\nタイキ先輩。",
            "enText": "Could I join you, Taiki?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "pathId": -1460326966322932975,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "……！\nイエス！　そーこなくっちゃデス！",
            "enText": "Y-Yes! I'd love to have ya!",
